name: CryptoMoss #35
description:
CryptoMoss #35 by @Vusiuz | Codename: Dragonfross | A glitchmoss from arid area, usually absorbing heat and ironsands greedily from it's surrounding, it has a same behaviour with CM #12, Furnace, but more solid

Cryptomoss is Random Living Moss Species that grow over Cryptoworld :D, Each number is created because accidentally randomized simulations that even the creator, @vusiuz cant even replicate again :D
